Body and Design

Citizen watches are reputed for their innovative style and out-of-the-box craftsmanship; this beautiful timepiece is no exception. A dazzling time wear this women’s analog wristwatch boasts of an enticing charm that will win you a lot of admiring glances at any social gathering. The elegance of the watch face is expressed in the tonneau shaped dial of this watch which is decorated in attractive hues.

The delicate dial is covered by a layer of mineral glass crystal which makes this beautiful timepiece resistant against scratches. The brilliant optical clarity of the glass allows the wearer to read time in this analog wristwatch for women from Citizen without hassles.

The Citizen analog watch for women is an epitome of feminine splendour; the presence of a steel case being another reason for its attractive appeal. The watch comes equipped with a stainless steel strap which keeps the timepiece fastened to your wrist without causing any irritation to the user. The strap will never let the Citizen wristwatch for women slip away from your hand courtesy of the presence of a fold over clasp.
